<para>Stores a functor of type: <computeroutput>void(void)</computeroutput>. Possibly stateful. Supported <computeroutput><ref refid="common_8h_1ac983b89bddb9b22c9b416f31399f0095" kindref="member">MR_PassBy</ref></computeroutput> modes: <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_DefaultConstruct</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_Copy</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_Move</computeroutput> (and <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_DefaultArgument</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_NoObject</computeroutput> if supported by the callee). </para>
